{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01J73kJB4fA9j9tZq8VGDrg2","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### 1. Loop task state tracking (`internal/host/loop.go`)\n- Added `TaskAssignment`, `TaskStateEntry` types for representing task pipeline state\n- Added `lastTasks` and `taskRuns` fields to `Loop` to cache fetched tasks and track task-to-run mappings\n- Added `GetTaskSnapshot()` method returning current tasks with assignment state (assigned/deduped status, run IDs)\n- Updated `pickTaskFromPhase()` and `pickTask()` to cache fetched tasks\n- Updated `runPhased()` goroutine to record run ID after main phase completes\n\n### 2. gRPC server (`internal/adapters/grpc/server.go`)\n- Added `GetLoopTasks(projectDir)` method that queries the loop for a project and converts `host.TaskStateEntry` to `web.TaskEntry` format\n- Added `web` import\n\n### 3. Web dashboard (`internal/adapters/web/handler.go`)\n- Added `TaskEntry` type (JSON-serializable task with assignment state)\n- Added `TaskProvider` interface with `GetLoopTasks(projectDir)` method\n- Added `WithTaskProvider()` handler option\n- Added `GET /api/projects/{name}/tasks` endpoint returning task pipeline state as JSON\n- `ClocheServer` satisfies `TaskProvider` interface\n\n### 4. Daemon wiring (`cmd/cloched/main.go`)\n- Passes the gRPC server as `TaskProvider` to the web handler\n\n### 5. CLI (`cmd/cloche/main.go`)\n- Added `cloche tasks [--project <dir>]` command\n- Calls the web HTTP API (same pattern as `logs --follow`)\n- Displays tasks in a formatted table: ID, STATUS, ASSIGNED, RUN, TITLE\n\n### 6. Tests\n- **Loop tests** (`internal/host/loop_test.go`): 4 new tests for `GetTaskSnapshot` covering empty state, phased loop, legacy assigner, and dedup expiry\n- **Web tests** (`internal/adapters/web/handler_test.go`): 4 new tests for tasks API endpoint covering tasks with provider, no provider, no loop, and project not found\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":305,"cache_read_input_tokens":120848,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":305},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6146b7bf-a511-4374-8899-2af97fce0332","uuid":"f77fe76a-e6a1-426e-866e-010e03d491cc"}
